➜【星连文学社】广东诗人辉哥：七夕
http://www.sohu.com/a/414706982_100115135	52833
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200824/f2c9e75220e143e897c5aa63791d7a3b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七夕</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/辉哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怨侣千年七夕传，鹊桥相会意熬煎；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真情自古多波劫，天上人间一样难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200824/60391f3836ca4678810eb99399d209bb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>围炉诗情辉哥，来自广东梅县客家，自小在客家农村长大，对客家文化情有独钟。喜爱古诗词，涂鸦作品多用于自耍。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200824/1520ebfdd7c04618aacb3c774cd45a84.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
